name: Subject A111.
description:
Ever since the day 'Subject A111' was exposed to "The Thing", he has killed the 5th clone of himself, the first one being killed on the second day. Subject is unable to control his cloning power. Clones of subject keeps attacking the real one to be the one remaining

Resulting in 'Subject A111" having to fight for his life. While resulting in huge physical and survival instinct improvements, subject is experiencing existential dread.

Experiments will be continued.
All instances of experiments objects are to be contained and quarantined until death.
